<view class="s-padding s-size">吐槽内容</view>
<view class='s-padding'>
 <textarea class='font-size-four' style='height:6rem;width:100%;' placeholder='请输入...' bindinput='onContent' maxlength="{{max}}"></textarea>
</view>
<view class='s-padding'>
<view class='flex-row space-between'>
<view></view>
<view class='sub-text'>{{content.length}}/{{max}}</view>
</view>
<view class='line'></view>
</view>

<view class='s-padding s-size'>上传图片</view>
<view class='s-padding flex-row align-center flex-wrap'>
    <view class='relative  icon-right' wx:for="{{images}}">
    <img  src="{{item}}" clazz="icon icon-add round  vertical-space"></img>    
            <image src='/r/circle_delete.png' class="icon arrow" style="position:absolute;right:-0.3rem;top:-0.3rem" bindtap='deleteContactImage' data-index="{{index}}"></image>
    </view>

    <image src='/r/add_image.png' class='icon icon-add vertical-space' bindtap='addImage'></image>

</view>
<view class='s-padding'>
      <view class=' hint-text wrap'>
  您好，您的需求“小优”将尽快处理。“小优”的工作时间是上午9:00—下午18:00，非工作时间如有紧急事宜请致电客户服务中心。
</view>
</view>
<bottom>
  <view class='bg-primary text-white center-text  s-size action-bar' bindtap='submit'>提交</view>
</bottom>